      </processinfo>
      <scopecontent id="aspace_a0896195dd9e93f014e7b2ddfcf06385">
         <head>Scope and Contents</head>
         <p>This finding aid encompasses accessions of materials pertaining to Alphonse Daudet. Material acquired before 1998 has been organized into two series:<ref actuate="onrequest" show="replace" target="ref10"> Series I, <title localtype="simple" render="italic">
                  <part>Letters from Alphonse Daudet</part>
               </title> 
            </ref>, and <ref actuate="onrequest" show="replace" target="ref23">Series II, <title localtype="simple" render="italic">
                  <part>Writings</part>
               </title> 
            </ref>. Material acquired after that date is located in <ref actuate="onrequest" show="replace" target="ref26">Series III, <title localtype="simple" render="italic">
                  <part>Additions Since January 1998</part>
               </title> 
            </ref>, which is arranged in accession order.</p>  
      </scopecontent>
      <bioghist id="aspace_e236f5ab3361b4961b654015b70b1f15">
         <head>Alphonse Daudet, 1840-1897</head>
         <p>Alphonse Daudet was a 19th century French novelist.</p>  
      </bioghist>
